      (e) confirm task 018's `file-preview` registry key resolves correctly
          (no console errors about unresolved widget type).
      If task 018 has not yet landed, document that the dispatch fires
      correctly but the Context pane renders its default empty/spinner state
      (graceful; not a defect).
    </step>
    <step order="8" name="Dark-Mode + Visual Regression Check">
      Toggle the SpaarkeAi shell theme (light → dark). Verify:
      (a) clickable `[n]` Button retains brand stroke + readable text in both
          themes (Fluent v9 tokens only);
      (b) non-clickable `[n]` span retains correct color in both themes;
      (c) clickable + non-clickable in the same response paragraph have
